  <chunk id="5bf6b6685fadbbc4899faa052321c697190bbade.c0" text="molecules 18α-Glycyrrhetinic Acid Induces Apoptosis of HL-60 Human Leukemia Cells through Caspases-and Mitochondria-Dependent Signaling Pathways">
